      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOOM PANTHER (5) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a second place finish (30.18) there the start prior. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. RAMIREZ MONELLI (2) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant fourth (30.53) in a Maiden over 520m at this track. Worth following up. WEST ON MIRRA (1) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing second (30.44) at this track in a Maiden over 520m. Overdue and is among the main hopes. GRAVITY MONELLI (8) cannot be underestimated.",
